{"tid":201720,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[神級] IVE 畢業生竟然可以係哈佛教書","createTime":"2017-04-15T03:45:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-15T15:13:59.000Z","uid":14170,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"02068721914e2b6bedf3fb57723617f21e250d66","tid":201720,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T03:45:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/57CuX57.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F57CuX57.png&h=f4b9ff9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nIVE 畢業 -&gt; HKU 教授 -&gt; 下年去哈佛教書<br />\n<br />\n一個誘人發憤的苦讀成材故事。Band 5學生、會考「2D、5E、1F」、重讀中五，換轉是現今任何一個青少年都可能會頓覺前路茫茫，甚至自暴自棄。梁美儀卻視此為人生轉捩點，把握眼前機會選擇投身當時尚是新興科目的環保科學，至此堅守信念拾級而上，終成為香港大學生物科學學院副教授及本年度十大傑青之一。他昨以自身經歷勉勵年輕人應努力訂立目標，發揮潛能。"},{"pid":"b303dd1b7db977a8294294d542f04e22a2a0d285","tid":201720,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T03:50:02.000Z","msg":"呢個係咪當年去左劍橋果個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d3ff73d9d2ccd9160f121f184a1c56af859bb00","tid":201720,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T04:25:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0caef80dc663019e54109f5f6ca15314a62607b9","tid":201720,"uid":60861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T04:26:11.000Z","msg":"ive都吹奏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"637d0fe6dc98de4855db74327181186cc07150dd","tid":201720,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T04:26:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個係咪當年去左劍橋果個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係，證明 IVE 人才輩出"},{"pid":"0381cbccef7c73cb1892e9a6d2badcd2523fa19b","tid":201720,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score